            [Gained Bane Lost 20 Zeal, 10 Bliss
            & 20 Flock]

'
        - weight: 20
          module:
          - rid: 107151359355650158
          output: "Ha! The play had the misfortune of opening on the same eve as
            a premiere directed by one of the Empire\u2019s greatest masters. It
            passed without glory or notice. Those who did attend mentioned it cast
            us in a poor light, but who cares? The Beholder smiles upon us!\r\n[Lost
            5 Bliss]\r\n"
